'''''NukeWar''''' is a 1980 video game by [[Avalon Hill]] for the [[Apple II]], [[Atari 8-bit computers]], [[Commodore 64]], [[Commodore PET]], [[FM-7]], [[TRS-80]], and [[VIC-20]].

==Gameplay==
''NukeWar'' is a game of global thermonuclear war represented by text and [[Sprite (computer graphics)|sprites]] on the screen.<ref name=cgw150/>

==Reception==
